<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA58">
<l>mikka muḻaṅkeriyum vīṅkiya poṅkiruḷu</l>
<l>mokka vuṭaṉiruntā lovvātē - cekkarpō</l>
<l>lākattāṉ ceñcaṭaiyu māṅkavaṉtaṉ poṉṉuruvil</l>
<l>pākattāḷ pūṅkuḻalum paṇpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If they are together so that the ample roaring fire and the swollen churning darkness are equal,</l>
<l>it does not agree with the quality of the flower curls</l>
<l>of her who is part of his golden form there, and of the red matted hair</l>
<l>of him with a body like the evening sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
